✅ Components in Your System Of Phase- 1
Component	Arduino Pin
Push Button	D7
Buzzer	D8
RGB LED - Red	D5 (PWM)
RGB LED - Green	D6 (PWM)
RGB LED - Blue	D3 (PWM)
DHT11 (Temp/Humidity)	D2
Soil Moisture Sensor	A0
NodeMCU TX → UNO RX	D0 (via voltage divider)
NodeMCU RX ← UNO TX	D1

⚠️ Note: Disconnect D0 and D1 (TX/RX) before uploading the sketch.
